other_tests.findings: Gallstones are in the gallbladder. Nonmobile echogenic structures on the gallbladder wall without internal vascularity likely reflect adherent sludge. Moderate to severe right hydronephrosis.
Mild leukocytosis to 11.8, plts of 148, Cr of 0.3, AST 26, ALT 15, Tbili 0.6, Amylase 56.
